{"tid":2279061,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"習近平致電孔戴 祝賀他再次當選幾內亞總統","createTime":"2020-11-09T13:49:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-10T00:14:55.000Z","uid":240362,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f87a6fc7a6d9e4205d9ad2a41dd5d7ebe3ed4383","tid":2279061,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T13:49:13.000Z","msg":"在北京，國家主席習近平致電孔戴，祝賀他再次當選幾內亞總統。<br />\n<br />\n《新華社》報道，習近平強調，高度重視中幾關係發展，願同孔戴一道努力，加強相互支持，造福兩國和兩國人民。<br />\n<br />\n較早前，幾內亞憲法法院確認，現任總統孔戴在10月18日舉行的總統選舉中獲勝，第三次當選幾內亞總統。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559147-20201109.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1559147-20201109.htm&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y7P2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=6b335e68\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1559147-20201109.htm&h=a48948a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559147-20201109.htm</a>"},{"pid":"995b66309d70cdca0b4882fbf6f9367771f42b9e","tid":2279061,"uid":76804,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T13:49:45.000Z","msg":"唔致電拜登?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d37c3c8f7bf34c6523e4b8bd150cf8a295e300d6","tid":2279061,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T13:49:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"833f67050fcf423ba71ec38f0eff70c3144cf074","tid":2279061,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T13:50:39.000Z","msg":"拜登呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"713765326777869142ffa6357717b35d3b748424","tid":2279061,"uid":152394,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T23:16:47.000Z","msg":"無拜登手提。。得白宮電話。。入到去先打俾佢"},